# Report

## EXISTING STRUCTURES

### Electricity generator at position(-18.5, 19.5)
Consists of steam engine (position -18.5, 19.5), boiler (position -13.5, 20.0), and offshore pump (position -11.5, 26.5).

### Lab at position(-17.5, 23.5)

### Pipe network

- PipeGroup (fluid_system=35502, position -18.5, 16.5)
- PipeGroup (fluid_system=35505, position -12.5, 21.5)

### Small Electric Poles

- Position (-16.5, 19.5)
- Position (-19.5, 22.5)

## ERROR TIPS

### Errors related to crafting items
- Ensure that all required ingredients are available in your inventory before attempting to craft items. In this case, iron plates are required to craft iron gear wheels.

### Errors when using extracting but being too far
- Make sure to move to the target entity where you want to extract from before extracting items.

### Errors when placing into a tile which is occupied by another entity
- Ensure you can place an entity to a tile before attempting to place it.

### Errors related to missing entities
- Check for the presence of required entities, such as stone furnaces, before attempting to perform actions that depend on them.
